  maxi
  Builtin Function



      [1mSynopsis[0m
        Maximum value indices

      [1mSyntax[0m
        maxi ( [4mA[24m )

      [1mDescription[0m
        Maxi returns the index of the maximum value contained in matrix.
        If the input argument ([4mA[24m) is a vector, then the index of the
        largest value is returned. If [4mA[24m is a MxN matrix, then a row-
        vector of the column indices of the largest column values of [4mA[0m
        is returned.


     [1mSee Also[0m
        max, min, mini













































